Silence::

She smiled and gave Kenzo a friendly and innocent wave of her hand.
"I'm the one called Silence. Pleased to meet you." in a slightly timid
voice. She felt a little uncomfortable with all the battle bots
around. FIghting was her fortay.  Recon was her field of expertice.
She had always been slightly intimidated by the warrior bots.  And no
matter how she tried to hide it, it still showed.
